title: Best of The Herd
itunes:title: Best of The Herd
description:
Colin admits the Broncos might have made a BIG mistake trading and paying huge money for Russell Wilson following another disappointing loss in primetime. He points out the biggest issue Aaron Rodgers and the Packers are having after falling to 3-3 on the season. He gives you his Herd Hierarchy after week 6 of the NFL season. Plus, Fox Sports NFL analyst Mark Sanchez joins the show in studio to talk about the struggling Denver offense and USC losing their first game of the season. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
